Analyst and Associate ShowdownFirst Annual Associate and Analyst Showdown Sponsored by EES will take place November in the Enron Building Lobby from This is your chance to play foosball air hockey and darts for prizes The tournament will be double or single elimination depending on the number of responses To participate please email Alexandra Saler by November Provide your name what sport you would like to play and team membersfor foosball only See You At The Showdown
